{"tid":1068683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【性別自主】同性戀歌手Sam Smith考慮做變性手術","createTime":"2019-03-19T11:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T14:00:55.000Z","uid":51546,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3b4ee2fe07aa16bfa807d85c3506e5a980e7c943","tid":1068683,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T11:45:22.000Z","msg":"憑《Stay with Me》、《Lay Me Down》以及《I'm Not The Only One》走紅全球樂壇的山姆史密斯，事業一帆風順，但他曾坦言小時候曾因為太胖而被霸凌，他受不了最後跑去抽脂，讓胸部看起來比較小一點。<br />\n<br />\nSam Smith日前接受訪問坦言體重一直是他最大的困擾：「我出道以來經常穿西裝，全想遮掩肥胖身體，不過在我後來減肥，練肌肉的過程，卻跟心底的女性化有極大衝突」，而他在10歲就已經出櫃，如今仍在性別定位中徬徨，目前還認真考慮想要變性：「我一度想要變性，一直到現在仍在考慮做手術。」"},{"pid":"2a2874ebdc6971f5b0b403c15a37c9bad06486ce","tid":1068683,"uid":131691,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T11:47:08.000Z","msg":"好好地搞基做乜走去切J造假閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdba518e6ef9c599738398e184504766f5916d98","tid":1068683,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"2a2874ebdc6971f5b0b403c15a37c9bad06486ce","tid":1068683,"uid":131691,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T11:47:08.000Z","msg":"好好地搞基做乜走去切J造假閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T11:51:43.000Z","msg":"每個基佬嘅夢想-擁有女性嘅身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39dcd4708f6f2a479520b28eadd2088df17d49b0","tid":1068683,"uid":59465,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"bdba518e6ef9c599738398e184504766f5916d98","tid":1068683,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"2a2874ebdc6971f5b0b403c15a37c9bad06486ce","tid":1068683,"uid":131691,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T11:47:08.000Z","msg":"好好地搞基做乜走去切J造假閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T11:51:43.000Z","msg":"每個基佬嘅夢想-擁有女性嘅身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" 